channel.title: Impulse Errors?
channel.description:
It was working fine for a few hours, then stopped all of a sudden.
Using rimmington powerminer btw (/rminePower(iron)), i tried draynor willows too (/dwcut(rune)!
I just turned it off, Tried Aryans. No luck. Just turned off Both, and turned Impulse back on, and it worked.
Does it only work for like 1.5 hours then just stops?
When it stopped my char stood there and did nothing. Randoms work nicely, even the myterious old man. Not sure what the problem might be.
Any ideas? :confused:

item.title: Impulse Errors?

I figured out its from disabling the graphics. just dont disable them and it works smooth.
